Marianne Jean-Baptiste https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marianne_Jean-Baptiste 0 Marianne Ragipcien Jean-Baptiste (born 26 April 1967) is an English actress, composer and director, best known for her roles as Hortense Cumberbatch in Secrets Lies (1996), for which she was nominated for the Academy Award for Best Supporting Actress, and as Vivian Johnson on the American television series Without a Trace. In 2015, she starred as Sharon Bishop QC in the ITV crime series Broadchurch.
